				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Simple unvoiced AD for the Farslayer. He regularly casts Power Word: Kill and is meant to be target number one in the fight (the others leave if he dies). The AD is meant to play on his first turn, and is there purely to draw attention to the players that the idea is to move forward and kill him to get past them."
				}
